title: Footprints discovered along a creek on a sand bar
observed: A footprint that was 11 1/2" long, 6" at the ball and 3" at the heel was discovered on a sandbar and cast. The cast indicated that the depth of the foot at the ball was two inches and the depth at the heel was one inch.
location_details: This took place near Warsaw, Ohio in Coshocton County, Ohio.
